  - [client/src/App.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/App.jsx)
  - [client/src/components/Header.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/components/Header.jsx)
  - [client/src/pages/AboutPage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/AboutPage.jsx)
  - [client/src/pages/AccessPage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/AccessPage.jsx)
  - [client/src/pages/CreatePage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/CreatePage.jsx)
  - [client/src/pages/FeedPage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/FeedPage.jsx)
