- **Test-Driven Router Scaffolding**: Before implementing the routes, constructed a Vitest integration test suite [client/src/__tests__/routing.test.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/__tests__/routing.test.jsx). Installed `@testing-library/user-event` to handle accurate route clicks and verification checks.

- **React Router Integration**:
  - Implemented `createBrowserRouter` via [client/src/router.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/router.jsx) containing paths for `/`, `/create`, `/logs/:id`, and `/profile/:username`.
  - Replaced the hardcoded routing component swap in [client/src/main.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/main.jsx) with the robust `<RouterProvider />`.
  
- **Layout & Placeholders**:
  - Implemented a persistent [Layout.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/components/Layout.jsx) wrapper that integrates the `NavBar` and `<Outlet />`, guaranteeing clean and flicker-less UI navigation. 
  - Constructed clean HTML placeholders for all primary route pages ([HomePage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/HomePage.jsx), [CreateLogPage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/CreateLogPage.jsx), [LogDetailPage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/LogDetailPage.jsx), [UserProfilePage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/UserProfilePage.jsx)), as well as a fallback [NotFoundPage.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/pages/NotFoundPage.jsx) for unregistered subdirectories.

## Validation Results
- **Automated Tests**: Completed execution of all front-end Vitest scripts, specifically validating dynamic path loading, URL link simulations, and the automated 404 response catch.
- **ESLint Validation**: Executed `npm run lint` across the front-end, successfully removing all TypeScript unexpected token parsing errors. Checkout the [.jsx](file:///Users/mineral/Desktop/VibeCoding/P2/cs7180_project2_collective-unconscious/client/src/App.jsx) syntax and zero warnings/errors.
